r />\n班師傅老早走哂出九龍灣啦 無零件不再話下 無車都夠膽死"},{"pid":"db49a33da81ac8f9e4b9cb0e2c38a4dfa16772e4","tid":284295,"uid":58791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>法拉利就爭住要<br />\n麥拿倫就冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實點解呢<br />\n照計個名都唔係差丫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有錢佬買咁貴既車都係想show與眾不同，但老麥玩性能由最低grade到最高grade部部都差唔多樣點買得落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無人買自然無人賣<br />\n<br />\n拉利都重係唔同model唔同樣咪重有市場，不過拉利最靚design既時間已經過去，而家D樣硬係覺得怪怪地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38d3e5093e9446256da1f76d3bdf463a3190943","tid":284295,"uid":16477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:01:45.000Z","msg":"blackbird既貨/拖車好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280ec0e68afec328c7035e60e323e5c82d0e3456","tid":284295,"uid":21259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T18:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>奇怪用開果個代理係咪好差？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係marketing方面唔係太差，不過整車嗰邊做得麻麻地，d師傅成日轉，訂零件又耐。因為岩岩依手代理其實唔係做左汽車行業好耐。佢老細本身搞金融，只係出錢買起左原本香港法拉利既代理公司。</blockquote><br />\n班師傅老早走哂出九龍灣啦 無零件不再話下 無車都夠膽死</blockquote><br />\n冇車即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9af139d58925ef81395b52622516713ba5f320","tid":284295,"uid":119896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T18:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係 Ceci Li 老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}